data.description: Introducing a stunning opportunity in the sought-after neighborhood of Spring Valley! This classy and spacious brick rancher is the epitome of elegance and comfort. Step inside and be greeted by the gleaming oak hardwood floors that adorn the living and dining rooms, exuding a timeless charm.  The kitchen is a testament to quality craftsmanship, featuring top-notch cabinetry that offers ample storage space for all your culinary needs. Picture yourself cozying up in the family room, surrounded by built-in bookshelves and a charming brick fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation and gatherings.  Outside, a fenced and private yard awaits, complete with a delightful patio. Enjoy lazy afternoons or entertain guests in this serene outdoor oasis. The meticulous owners have spared no expense in maintaining this property, evident from the beautiful landscaping showcasing burning bush, hydrangeas, roses, and crepe myrtle.  This home also boasts a separate dining room adorned with an exquisite Italian crystal chandelier, setting the stage for elegant meals and special occasions. The oversized 2-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage, ensuring convenience and organization.  The basement is a hidden gem, offering a vast recreational room that can be tailored to your preferences and needs. Additionally, the house features a heated paved driveway to ease the winter months.  The owners have taken great care to update this property, including a new roof installed just three years ago, updated soffit and gutters, a recently replaced water heater and recently replaced HVAC units (3 yrs. ago). The blown insulation ensures energy efficiency, while the meticulous landscaping adds a touch of beauty to the exterior.  Don't miss your chance to own this meticulously maintained and thoughtfully improved home in Spring Valley. Schedule your private tour today and discover the endless possibilities that await you!
